{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 1316266, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 258889, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "资本强势的社会主义", "timestamp": 1616475136, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1316269, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 258889, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "当然不是，最基本的，资本家有没有控制政治？所有制关系怎么样。", "timestamp": 1616475171, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1316270, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 258889, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "没有标准答案吧", "timestamp": 1616475212, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1316274, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 258889, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: wfm的暗号么hhh", "timestamp": 1616475257, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1316282, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 258889, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "資本家尚未形成有統一政治訴求的階級", "timestamp": 1616475374, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1316284, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 258889, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "em资本主义也不是说“资本家控制政治”吧", "timestamp": 1616475385, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1316285, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 258889, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "资社二分的分法是不是已经过时了", "timestamp": 1616475402, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1316286, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 258889, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 这倒是", "timestamp": 1616475405, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1316287, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 258889, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 嗯", "timestamp": 1616475417, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1316291, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 258889, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "威权资本主义", "timestamp": 1616475477, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1316310, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 258889, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "资本强势，懂的都懂", "timestamp": 1616475639, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1316311, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 258889, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 从来不是二分啊，咋学的🐎主义...", "timestamp": 1616475651, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1316315, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 258889, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 威权一词是冷战意识形态战中西方特指社会主义的，你这太糅合了", "timestamp": 1616475728, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1316320, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 258889, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "这个社会上是何种阶级占据主导地位？是工农吗？工农的话语权和社会地位体现在何处？无产阶级占据主要力量和政治地位才可以说是社会主义。", "timestamp": 1616475772, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1316321, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 258889, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 在中国历史上很长一段时间里，资社就是二分的。后来才有人明白，很多东西，既不姓资又不姓社，姓资姓社不争论", "timestamp": 1616475773, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1316330, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 258889, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "自信点，把……去掉", "timestamp": 1616475838, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1316340, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Jason", "pid": 258889, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 不是，Authorian的概念出现的甚至比proletariat（无产者）的概念还要早，是在罗马时代就已经是指向帝国式的Kaiser专政和压制范式，后经卢梭、卡尔·马克思、韦伯、列宁等人的发展指向了现今的含义", "timestamp": 1616475953, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1316356, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Jason", "pid": 258889, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "以Jason来看，就是一个Authorian Capitalism的结构，但是不同的是，这一资本主义并非是自发地产生的，而是自为地由党的主体实践而来的——因此它从出生开始就摒弃了资本主义一开始不发展时对“自由”、“民主”的追求，成为了最为自为的，仅仅为增殖而增殖的资本主义", "timestamp": 1616476089, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1316357, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 258889, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "中国有点封建社会残余加资本主义的感觉。中国大资本家仍然是官僚系统的附庸", "timestamp": 1616476104, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1316362, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Jason", "pid": 258889, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "简单地讲，谁更资：\nA.降点工资都要被左翼党派、工会、媒体gank\nB.打个电话就能把工人碾送二刺螈", "timestamp": 1616476160, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1316378, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Kate", "pid": 258889, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "官僚资产阶级难道没有形成吗？国家的经济命脉就是由官僚主导的垄断资产阶级控制的啊", "timestamp": 1616476358, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1341517, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Louis", "pid": 258889, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "其实是的。只不过中国当今资本主义的形成与西方国家的形成方式不同。西方国家的资本主义国家的形成是由于资产阶级在封建社会自下而上革命形成的，国家机器受到资本的控制；而咱们国家的资本主义的形成是由国家发起的，资本主义是受到国家机器控制的资本主义，是自上而下发起的。这也决定了咱们国家当今的资产阶级的政治诉求尚不完善，而且政权中心掌握在中央手中，而不是资产阶级手中。但按照当今的情况，中央权力基本集中到了中央领导人个人，可以说是有种帝制控制下的资本主义的味道。总之要说真正的社会主义，就算有一点，也基本没啥影子了。", "timestamp": 1616829802, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 12, "pid": 258889, "reply": 22, "tag": "政治相关", "text": "所以，中国到底是不是“变相的资本主义”呢？越准备材料越没底……", "timestamp": 1616475090, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1616829801, "url": "", "vote": {}}}